<h3>About DIY</h3>
<p>The best person to show them how is another kid. DIY is a safe online community for kids to discover new skills, meet friends who are geeks just like them, and be awesome.</p>

<h3>Kid Passions SVG Animation</h3>
<p>Kid passions had one goal in mind; subtle and simplistic. Each orb circling the child must be subtle in movement and randomly emit waves to the brain thereby sending a signal down the body. The final touches would be eye movement and breathing to further portray a sense of realism.</p>

