<h3>Underneath SVG Animation</h3>
<p>Using the following illustration by <a href="http://www.isaiahsaxon.com">Isaiah Saxon</a>, it was requested to create an animation sequence that was subtle and sparked curiousity. What makes this animation are the little intricate pieces to discover. The arm bend, the bugs moving, the rock lifting, the foot wiggle and much more are the key ingredients to this entire sequence</p>

