<h3>Challenges</h3>
<p>Underneath was one of those projects that comes along where ambivalence sets in but luckily the desire to work on such an amazing project made everything all better. Since the graphic was originally created in Photoshop meant it had to be converted to vector in order to animate.</p>

<p>It was decided that in order to find the most efficient possible method that would also result in the most likeness to the original to use tracing option in Illustrator.</p>

